{"tid":2404735,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西貢海濱公園紙船雕塑　「香港」、「獨立」字眼被遮　康文署指為點綴環境","createTime":"2021-02-12T01:57:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T02:33:33.000Z","uid":36494,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f1427566b7cf99b698b33fa28130e55c0bf7a5b0","tid":2404735,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T01:57:03.000Z","msg":"眾新聞<br />\n<br />\n西貢海濱公園紙船雕塑　「香港」、「獨立」字眼被遮　康文署指為點綴環境】<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">西貢海濱公園內的水池廣場，由2003年起一直放置紙船雕塑，其中一隻船的圖樣來自大公報抗日新聞剪報，剛巧在角落顯示了「香港」、「獨立」字眼。近日康文署將紙船雕塑改成花槽，又額外加設花盆遮蓋有關字眼。</span><br />\n<br />\n康文署回覆眾新聞查詢指，紙船上其中一段提到的文字，剪報原文標題內容為「東江縱隊港九獨立大隊---日軍侵佔香港時期一支堅持武裝」。署方又稱，每逢農曆新年期間均會揀選轄下的康樂場地加以佈置，以增添節日氣氛，擺設不同盆栽花卉作為新年裝飾，是為了點綴公園周圍的環境。 <br />\n<br />\n昨日，Facebook專頁空城記在網上發文，表示「紙船屹立多年已經甩色一段時間，上個月去睇都仲好地地，今個月去睇除咗補過油，仲有唔知邊個天才去諗將隻船變做花槽，然後最重要係再塞多幾個花槽係出面，順便遮走果幾隻字。」<br />\n<br />\n(圖片來源︰「空城記 Empty City」facebook專頁)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k2xbdAb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk2xbdAb.jpg&h=58ab9403&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b73d9ed01b8d3e0f6b037b242982f8dac574358d","tid":2404735,"uid":36494,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T01:58:34.000Z","msg":"大公報宣傳港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"724f2d8f23851e32dae8f75b8c30c548a1104783","tid":2404735,"uid":375641,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T01:58:59.000Z","msg":"加舊唔襯嘅野都叫點綴？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"617fc015457520a235442ae46b70e000f9861d07","tid":2404735,"uid":96486,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"724f2d8f23851e32dae8f75b8c30c548a1104783","tid":2404735,"uid":375641,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T01:58:59.000Z","msg":"加舊唔襯嘅野都叫點綴？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:13:06.000Z","msg":"其實政府依家做野好多既目得都心照不宣.."},{"pid":"896907a54fc2aa71e98d19014f9aab1c13151bbe","tid":2404735,"uid":33443,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:20:02.000Z","msg":"遍地開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />康文署居心叵測<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c23c2ceaa03e465879639400a7d6b4c3d7fba58c","tid":2404735,"uid":64073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:32:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba380cdaa45e49659bd2ccc3c78702aa3b3a36d8","tid":2404735,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:33:33.000Z","msg":"此地無銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}